{"title":"游击队员们在舞蹈","authors":["哈吉·雅新"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击队员们在舞蹈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔阿尔及利亚〕哈吉·雅新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在篝火的光亮里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们跳着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄壮的舞蹈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而周围——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既无茅草的小房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又无少女的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有山地的雪松亭亭玉立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摆出庄严的姿态，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们眺望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在篝火的光亮里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们跳着阿尔及利亚愤怒的舞蹈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这跳动的火焰中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天正在诞生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切罪恶的、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚伪的东西都在死亡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而新生的橄榄树啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在村子的废墟上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地喧响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔张采译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}